            "Title": "S3 general purpose buckets should have Object Lock enabled",
            "Description": "This control checks whether an Amazon S3 general purpose bucket has Object Lock enabled. The control fails if Object Lock isn’t enabled for the bucket. If you provide a custom value for the 'mode' parameter, the control passes only if S3 Object Lock uses the specified retention mode.",
            "Remediation": {
                "Recommendation": {
                    "Text": "For information on how to correct this issue, consult the AWS Security Hub controls documentation.",
                    "Url": "https://docs.aws.amazon.com/console/securityhub/S3.15/remediation"
                }
            },
            "ProductFields": {
